ss=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：搞手 好撚想喺個group到講不如以後都唔好再約 跟手退group 但又做唔出 經常懷疑念舊既得翻我一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>或者得返巴打你一個仲念舊 其他都<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n被迫要人際關係變差 我仲成日講笑話我光榮孤立自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69ea448781d66ae49fa6581c1d3f7fe0dd43fee","tid":507522,"uid":152123,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T13:41:23.000Z","msg":"我嫲係我細個嘅時候講<br />\n唔好成日掛住同朋友玩<br />\n唔好因為朋友唔高興而扭曲自己<br />\n因為最後大部份朋友都唔會陪你過世<br />\n到頭來你會發現 只有屋企人先會陪你走落去 包括你第時嘅伴侶同仔女<br />\n<br />\n細個覺得我嫲誇張<br />\n大個望翻 原來係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08c8f687266334243421b083e532da32d6826fa2","tid":507522,"uid":140484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T13:42:58.000Z","msg":"same<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6330b61a1f735e538f2a1da5cc88d795c8b2658","tid":507522,"uid":122516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T13:49:28.000Z","msg":"主要係，無利用價值，所以無朋友"},{"pid":"1ac608ec9047494341cd6b9cff81027486de26da","tid":507522,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T13:50:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以前試過一排射鎖匙圈 上吓籃咁<br />\n但隔離人地就成班朋友打緊<br />\n之後慢慢就無打 停咗幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打番啦 有益健康 挑戰自己射3分</blockquote>可能遲啲買返個波落去打 <br />\n3分一直都好撚廢<br />\n不過而家最想打返羽毛球 想懷念吓讀書個陣同老友打波<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n...羽毛球冇人陪你打<br />\n你有冇ig呀<br />\n一打多d籃球 每打一次就貼上限時動態<br />\n可能之後會有人聊你打</blockquote>有時都有啲阿叔會一齊打吓嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你睇唔到我既重點<br />\n重點係po出黎等人聊你一齊打</blockquote>個啲fd list得屋企人同熟嘅朋友,數埋都無十個<br />\n有時同啲唔識嘅阿叔打都幾得意嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nbtw可能阿叔十幾年前exactly就你依個情況 直到依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d02623f3ef9ebe0ecebc1b4e7e14e0db139276a7","tid":507522,"uid":38540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T13:53:08.000Z","msg":"要keep其實係雙向 仲要人夾人<br />\n兩個一齊既時候係舒服有大把計傾唔駛做面具人講真話都係得一個老死可以咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fba12b61c9a7c16b6d022d75cc7c5b018d3c573c","tid":507522,"uid":47954,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T13:58:46.000Z","msg":"女裝、hehe 係唯一出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db968c48924cdcfe4ee65ba25056798a4ce8f09","tid":507522,"uid":150720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T14:00:16.000Z","msg":"you are not alone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca2c4fae434bdcec6db2e27d87d6ae3f9c99c03","tid":507522,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T14:01:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab1cb98dd3927e395a3035f34849aa93b2158f4","tid":507522,"uid":38077,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T14:02:36.000Z","msg":"一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點算好"},{"pid":"158b07e1dc2ccf04b7ae8f1ec9491bcdd5f1bce2","tid":507522,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T14:25:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1fc32b51fffbea16d53652c1e081a0beeb179f0","tid":507522,"uid":41818,"like":0,