5:19:57.000Z","msg":"唔知點解自己係想搵d 會傾到心事，深交嘅人，而唔係好似人地剩係傾去邊到玩，一傾到深入嘅就唔會搵到人同你傾。<br />\n<br />\n而且真係想玩自己一個又唔覺有咩問題，打波咪自己打，何必一定要有人陪先打到。慢慢就咩朋友都冇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能毒撚本原就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，鍾意自己一個多"},{"pid":"52aedb0fbfc6fc59caf153db562d82850560e0a8","tid":507522,"uid":30694,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T15:28:03.000Z","msg":"已經冇朋友咁滯，習慣晒，每日返工放工食飯瞓覺，人生就係咁過<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95eb9c884e63ba43107f971054c668d75be5b446","tid":507522,"uid":98143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T15:41:11.000Z","msg":"我都係返工一粒聲都唔出 比人話就死忍 利申 有女朋友"},{"pid":"5336897c1ac0882b6525a0d1e9756da073e944c6","tid":507522,"uid":10279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"52aedb0fbfc6fc59caf153db562d82850560e0a8","tid":507522,"uid":30694,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T15:28:03.000Z","msg":"已經冇朋友咁滯，習慣晒，每日返工放工食飯瞓覺，人生就係咁過<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T16:25:09.000Z","msg":"我咪又係咁真係 呢幾日都係好似平時咁番工放工食飯打機瞓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad705ee3f993270e1f69075213ed9b1a413a2c4","tid":507522,"uid":152788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T16:38:08.000Z","msg":"#metoo"},{"pid":"a218eda03229bc3ddb9f2d6150bfe19b136ab60f","tid":507522,"uid":134484,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T16:43:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3f288e646c87b3503f1ce5b6660c6ea8f275674","tid":507522,"uid":67447,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T17:01:33.000Z","msg":"我ig好多朋友相 全部一堆堆 個個以為我好多朋友 但其實一年都約唔到一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有個朋友每個月都話約我 話等手頭上既野做完就同我去街 我等了又等 係咁wtsap問佢約幾時 都唔覆我 睇都唔睇 但轉個頭ig又po同其他閨蜜去街既相 約多2次我都放棄唔理佢算了<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似求佢去街咁"},{"pid":"bf37497f5d0288605ae9f5fa9907ec7e03adaee2","tid":507522,"uid":163286,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T17:56:47.000Z","msg":"原來有咁多人都同樣情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中學同學一個都冇聯絡，成日見到佢地搞gathering ,但係就冇搵我，原來以前自己on9，自以爲係同佢地好熟。<br />\n第一份工啲同事都做到朋友，後尾都各散東西。之後既工就見識到人性既醜陋，體驗到人係幾咁自私，係你面前一套，係你背後批評你，我都怕撚左佢地，閒聊都吾想講。"},{"pid":"06f4f272aebfe6a851d1dcf90e6f3d604f821fa3","tid":507522,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T18:35:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來有咁多人都同樣情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中學同學一個都冇聯絡，成日見到佢地搞gathering ,但係就冇搵我，原來以前自己on9，自以爲係同佢地好熟。<br />\n第一份工啲同事都做到朋友，後尾都各散東西。之後既工就見識到人性既醜陋，體驗到人係幾咁自私，<span style=\"color: red;\">係你面前一套，係你背後批評你</span>，我都怕撚左佢地，閒聊都吾想講。</blockquote><br />\n其實就算係朋友都會係咁"},{"pid":"08352f2bfead483c970e58e1231ffa1c4470936b","tid":507522,"uid":122516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T11:09:09.000Z","msg":"因為你無利用價值，所以無朋友"},{"pid":"94236d058edb52ff3dd7abde5750ac24f798a6f1","tid":507522,"uid":38077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T14:43:46.000Z","msg":"好灰 每日都好驚lunch time<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最希望返工撞唔到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd02bc76815e1b4c2879cae31a1f28ac70788140","tid":507522,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08352f2bfead483c970e58e1231ffa1c4470936b","tid":507522,"uid":122516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T11:09:09.000Z","msg":"因為你無利用價值，所以無朋友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T18:27:04.000Z","msg":"正確"},{"pid":"ca901b36e9d546dcf8f0b8674a3699d5e10b4492","tid":507522,"uid":46124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":